                         GAME HINTS AND TIPS

TYPED IN BY PARASITE OF LSD.


SHADOW OF THE BEAST 1 SOLUTION
From the first key go right, get the bottle, go left, down the ladder,
right, up, up, right, down, left, up, left, down, left, up, get
bottle, left, down, down, right, kill the big monster, go through the
door, and climb to the top of the well. Now go right to kill the beast
lord.
On the PARANOMIA version, for infinate energy, wait for the lasat
title screen, to appear, then hold down the joystick fire button, and
the left mouse button until you have to change disk.

IT CAME FROM THE DESERT
The Queen ants hideout is in M1, near th mines, but you can't get to
it until you've killed the other ants.

BARBARIAN
On the title screen type 04 08 59 for infinate energy. During play,
roll your opponent into a corner then stand up and kick him until he
dies.

WEIRD DREAMS
For infinate lives go halfway through a mirror in th hallway and tap
out SOS on the HELP key, (... --- ...).
